name: Telos International
tag_list: game-developer, virtual-world, online-games, entertainment, animation, videogames, online-shopping, nintendo, wii, iphone, mmog, mmosg
overview:
Telos International is a game developer. Their latest game due out in June 2009 will be the City of Sinners & Saints. It will be a massive multi-player online social networking game where virtual travelers can enter a comedic, cartoon world.

Check out the City of Sinners & Saints trailer and enter the comedic, cartoon world. http://www.cityofsinnersandsaints.com

provider.name: Vision Quest, Lyles Center Fresno, Multiverse
